</div></div></section></section><section id="floats-group1" class="floats-group"><section class="bt xbox font-sm" id="BX1"><h2 class="obj_head">Highlights.</h2>
<ul id="L2" class="list" style="list-style-type:disc">
<li><p id="P77">Improving signal detection is key to strengthening drug safety surveillance</p></li>
<li><p id="P78">Multimodal signal detection (MSD) is based on jointly analyzing multiple data sources</p></li>
<li><p id="P79">This manuscript broadens evaluations of MSD done in prior studies</p></li>
<li><p id="P80">The results provide support for MSD, but its ultimate utility cannot currently be proven</p></li>
<li><p id="P81">Further research is needed to determine the ultimate utility of MSD</p></li>
</ul></section></section><section id="S25" class="ack"><h2 class="pmc_sec_title">ACKNOWLEDGMENTS</h2>
